Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,THE TERRIFYING DRACONIC AURA
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When this Dragon Crest shines,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,my body is enveloped in a current of\Nlife energy called a Draconic Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.29,0:02:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Defense Shroud that hardens my body\Nlike steel and repels all spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. That explains it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When that crest shined, Dai's body\Nbecame unbelievably hard.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I fully deploy this Draconic Aura\Nand fight using its power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,no creature in the world can face me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, you can no longer fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.57,0:03:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a wound.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is what Gigabreak does.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai, hang in there!\NYou're a Hero, aren't you?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:04:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic doesn't work,\Nso I'll hit you with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm like a frog being glared at\Nby a snake! I feel paralyzed!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I thoroughly crushed Crocodine\Nis because his type is the most dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.04,0:04:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The Draconic Aura repels all spells,\Nbut a greater force or Aura can pierce it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and damage my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you sure you want\Nto give away your weakness like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Young fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine is mighty. A strike from\Na weak Mage like you will hardly tickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, your arm would likely break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll still have to try!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is crazy, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But Popp is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp is going to get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Meruru... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I said leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't win in that condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have my left arm.\NThere's still hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I lose both my eyes,\NI'll still have my inner eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The inner eye you helped clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In that fight in Romos...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you risked your life to face me,\Nsomeone you couldn't hope to beat.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You showed me the greatness\Nof humans, trusting and fighting together.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who cleared\Nthe filth staining my heart, Popp,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:05:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I risk my life, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran may be unbeatable, but I can't\Ncall myself your friend if I do nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks, Big Guy.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But you don't have to die alone!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We die together!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes, Baran!\NThis will be my final attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool. Dodging an attack\Nfrom you now would be child's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I doubt you could dodge this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Gigabreak?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I held back earlier against Dino,\Nbut not this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Former colleague or not, I won't let you\Ncall humans great and live!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What an aura of wrath!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That was him holding back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll reduce both of you to ash!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It... It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai's back in action!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I cast Behoma! He's at full stamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And what difference will it make?!\NI'll just blow you all away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Gigaden!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine, look where I aim\Nand use that attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Aban Strash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:08:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Beast King Redemption Blast!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all right, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eye. Did he get your eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona! We need you\Nto look at Crocodine's eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Meruru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. Just his eyelid was cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two still doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted us to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But this one insisted on helping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:09:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do basic heal spells, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't!\NLeave the healing to Leona and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai's right, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe if it were someone else, but\Nwe're fighting to world's strongest man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, after being hit\Nby an attack like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He fully deployed his Draconic Aura\Nto protect his whole body!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's unhurt after taking both Aban Strash\Nand Beast King Redemption Blast...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we supposed to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The same red blood that we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Impossible.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:10:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They pierced my Draconic Aura\Nand damaged my body!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even with help from his friends,\Nfor such a small child...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it wasn't just his power.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The power of his friends\Nhad a large influence.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai's friends risked their lives\Nand did everything they could.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.07,0:10:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In turn, Dai's compassion for his friends,\Nmade his heart multiply his power.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unless that bond is broken,\NDai's power will continue to grow.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He may even be a threat to me eventually.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine, it looks like\Nour attacks had an effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. Either he falls or we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We just fight on until we're spent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, the same trick\Nwon't work twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't avoid my Gigabreak\Nwith such tricks again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:11:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But you never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy holds terrifying potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I shall use all my focus\Nto take the source of Dai's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,His Aura is gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he up to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?!\NMy crest is acting on its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that noise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Their Dragon Crests are resonating!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:02.38,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}BEAST KING REDEMPTION BLAST{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:07.39,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}GIGABREAK{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My head... My head is splitting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa Burasu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Gomechan... and everybody from the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this all flashing in my mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran, what have you done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I've taken what my son no longer needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.82,0:13:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've used too much of my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I must retreat for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall return to reclaim Dino.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are we safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.43,0:13:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, what a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You look dazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Who... are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did Baran just leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't have given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I got food, medicinal herbs,\Nand other things we might need.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. It's a real help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But wasn't it hard\Nwith the country in chaos?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't. It was the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was shut inside\Nor praying to the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like the country was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously? After what just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the sort of place Teran is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all people who know nothing\Nbut to worship and pray to the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who can blame them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:15:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like to do a little praying\Nof our own right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.31,0:15:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it look, Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine's eye should heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're cute. What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here. Be my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's total amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran said he took what Dai doesn't need.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He meant Dai's memories as a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that was some spell\Nthat takes memories away?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was probably an attack\Nusing the resonance of Dragon Crests.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:16:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He focused all of his energy\Nand funneled it all into Dai's brain.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai was too young to handle\NBaran's massive energy and was blown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, Dai's memory was erased\Nleaving his mind a blank slate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can he be cured?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But right now, Dai is like an infant.\NIf Baran attacks us now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more important is that\Nthe memories of us in Dai's head is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Dai.\NDo you really not remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You all keep calling me "Dai."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! You're Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You lived on Dermline Island with monsters\Nand you dreamed of being a future Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And there... And there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you met me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dermline Island... Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My head... hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Put this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...! Have you even\Nforgotten my name, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Master Aban who died to save us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts! You're hurting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! Take this sword! And remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember your greatest attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You mastered Aban Strash! Something even\Na genius like Hyunckel couldn't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brain may not remember,\Nbut your body has to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Swords scare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it! Do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Be it Earth Slash or Wave Slash...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That man scares me! He's bullying me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's hopeless.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With Dai like this...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.54,0:18:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}when Baran attacks again...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we'll be powerless!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.98,0:19:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell is Baran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only did he fail to capture Dai,\Nhe hasn't reported back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew we couldn't leave this to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that was a brilliant move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,To cut the bond between Dai\Nand his friends and render him useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.33,0:19:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And now it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The next battle will be one to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Baran will gather\Nall the forces he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Alert! Alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran has been located!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The southern tip of Bengana Kingdom.\NHe's been recuperating at Argo Point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Showing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those three colored bonfires?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's summoning the Dragon Masters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran is unmatched even when using\NDragons alone, so it's not widely known,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but he has three powerful servants\Ncalled the Dragon Masters.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I summon you, masters of the Three Fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It is time for the Dragon Legion\Nto go to battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.23,0:20:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dragon Masters are
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,powerful Dragon Riders\Nwho control Dragons of land, sea, and sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When they gather under Baran, their\Ndestructive power defies imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He controls such servants?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's pulling out all the stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:21:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So much for your chances, Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Dragon Masters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Member of the Dragon Masters,\NSky Rider Galdandy is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.70,0:21:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,King of the Sea,\NSea Rider Borahorn has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Land Rider Larhart at your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We await your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.00,0:22:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kindness is the magic of kind people{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.00,0:22:25.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yasashisa wa yasashii hito ga tsukaeru mahou{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.92,0:22:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then do I have no choice\NBut to just be a normal person?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.92,0:22:32.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jaa boku wa tada no hito de iru shikanaino?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.93,0:22:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.93,0:22:35.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doudarou{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.27,0:22:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if the place I call home may change{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.27,0:22:43.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kaeru basho wa ne kawatte yuku kedo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.11,0:22:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to me, Mother{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.11,0:22:46.49,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa kaasan boku wa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.65,0:22:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will never change those I protect{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.65,0:22:52.62,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mamoru hito wo kaetari shinai{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.08,0:22:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what you'd say{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.08,0:22:57.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}anata wa nannte iukana{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.45,0:23:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times I can be cowardly and small{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.45,0:23:01.50,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tokiyori yowaki de chippoke de{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.67,0:23:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would you say to me\NAs I hesitate to even hesitate?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.67,0:23:07.97,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mayou koto ni mo mayou boku ni nannte iukana{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike the today that I sought{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:13.80,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sagashite ita kyou to chigatte{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.97,0:23:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure you'd laugh at my disappointment{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.97,0:23:19.10,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ochikonnde shimau boku wo warau no darou{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.20,0:23:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The three Dragon Masters\Ngather under Baran.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.99,0:23:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together with Baran, they head\Nto Teran Kingdom to reclaim Dai.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.04,0:23:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Dai remains without his memory.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.63,0:23:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The panic and uncertainty\Ncreates cracks among his friends.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.25,0:23:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Baran and the Dragon Masters\Nadvance without mercy.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.55,0:23:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But one man makes his way toward them.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.34,0:23:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.76,0:23:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Dragon Masters Approach!"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.68,0:23:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i}
